1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All the sorrow between us.

2
00:01:36,759 --> 00:01:37,680
Master Fang.

3
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,600
Miss Su.

4
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,570
Master Fang.

5
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:49,920
My Lords.

6
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,720
Since you are friends of my boss,

7
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:54,080
you are naturally friends of mine.

8
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,320
Please wait a moment.

9
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,050
What is going on?

10
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:04,160
Heiyu is Song Wanniang's trusted aide.

11
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:05,640
On the day of the fire,

12
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:09,380
Song Wanniang and Brother Jian gave the evidence to Heiyu.

13
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,360
This is it.

14
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,920
Master Fang, Miss Su,

15
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,620
I have delivered the item.

16
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:26,540
You two can return to the capital to uphold justice.

17
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,880
I will take my brothers

18
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,280
and rush back overnight.

19
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,680
If you return to the capital, Miss Su,

20
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,720
please tell Qingniang for me

21
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,780
that I will wait for her at Qiufeng Ridge.

22
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,560
Thank you for your hard work.

23
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,120
Farewell.

24
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,050
He is a man of great loyalty.

25
00:02:58,079 --> 00:03:00,340
If he knew that Qingniang has already...

26
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:06,080
You should open it.

27
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,800
Okay.

28
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,440
My mother embroidered this herself.

29
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,800
So whenever I miss her,

30
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,000
I draw the Qilin on it myself.

31
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:32,840
This is paper from the Qin family.

32
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:38,280
It really is the teacher.

33
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:42,960
Master.

34
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:45,720
A secret letter arrived by carrier pigeon.

35
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,560
You may leave.

36
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,450
Yes, Master.

37
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,079
Come in.

38
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,040
Shadow sent word that

39
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:22,160
Su Zhaoxue and Fang Ji

40
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,960
might find the evidence.

41
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,560
Master, what should we do?

42
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,160
Send word to them.

43
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,960
No matter what,

44
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:34,440
they must get that evidence for me.

45
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:36,570
Yes, Master.

46
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:09,000
The Little Marquis has escorted Lord Fang's prison cart into the capital.

47
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,530
We should get going as well.

48
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,680
Where is Pihu?

49
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:15,520
Master Pihu said something came up, so he went ahead.

50
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,320
Move faster. We need to arrive before dark.

51
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:33,560
Greetings, Lord Fang.

52
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,280
Greetings, Miss Su.

53
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,680
Pihu, why are you here?

54
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:45,720
I learned that those letters have fallen into your hands.

55
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:48,360
Please hand them over to me.

56
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,960
Who sent you?

57
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,960
At this point,

58
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,720
it doesn't matter who sent me.

59
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,159
Pihu.

60
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,840
You actually betrayed the Little Marquis.

61
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,440
He treats you like a brother.

62
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,680
Yet you're willing to be a villain's lackey.

63
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,810
How can you face him?

64
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,240
I only hope

65
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:12,160
you two won't make things difficult for me.

66
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,200
Insolent!

67
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,880
Since you two don't appreciate the favor,

68
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,520
don't blame me

69
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,720
for being rude.

70
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,440
Teacher.

71
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,320
It really is these.

72
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,840
Mengniang,

73
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:35,120
please watch over me from heaven

74
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:42,120
and bless my great undertaking.

75
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:45,880
Teacher.

76
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:50,560
Allow me to congratulate you in advance on fulfilling your long-held wish.

77
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,360
My good disciple.

78
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:59,960
You've worked hard as the Qin family's shadow these years.

79
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,240
It was my duty.

80
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:06,600
If you hadn't saved me back then,

81
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,600
how could a child like me survive the famine?

82
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,720
Even if you wanted my life,

83
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:15,120
I wouldn't hesitate.

84
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:21,240
Now that it's all over,

85
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,400
you should get some proper rest.

86
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:29,640
Your wife and child are waiting for you at home.

87
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,200
Pi Hu.

88
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,280
Pi Hu.

89
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,760
What exactly is going on?

90
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,000
What happened?

91
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,520
I killed him.

92
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:14,000
Pi Hu was like a brother to me.

93
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,200
How could you do it?

94
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,600
He knew too many secrets.

95
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:24,560
It was to ensure nothing went wrong.

96
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,920
What about me?

97
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,720
I know all your secrets now.

98
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:35,240
Are you going to kill me too?

99
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,440
Ruilang.

100
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,720
You are my own son.

101
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:43,120
How could I ever hurt you?

102
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:46,520
Great men do not concern themselves with trifles.

103
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:49,560
You must learn to make sacrifices.

104
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:53,240
Do you want something to go wrong in the end

105
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,530
and fail when success is within reach?

106
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:59,320
When our great cause is achieved

107
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:02,200
and the Fang family is destroyed,

108
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:06,040
no one will fight you for the one you desire.

109
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:07,720
Remember.

110
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:10,440
You must be ruthless.

111
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,320
I don't want you

112
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:18,000
to repeat the mistakes your mother and I made.

113
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,760
Do you understand?

114
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:50,840
Fangji.

115
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,040
Fangji.

116
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:54,880
Fangji.

117
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,340
Fangji, are you all right?

118
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,680
Fangji.

119
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,000
Zhaoxue.

120
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,480
Fangji.

121
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,080
Here.

122
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:45,170
Easy now.

123
00:11:59,120 --> 00:11:59,920
Wait a moment.

124
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,250
I'll get you some herbs.

125
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:14,760
When did you learn to prepare medicine?

126
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:19,360
I watched Imperial Physician Hu treating people recently,

127
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:23,200
and I thought it might come in handy when roaming the world,

128
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,690
so I picked up a few tricks from him.

129
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:26,600
Zhaoxue.

130
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,800
I won't let you wander the world.

131
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,160
I'll always be with you,

132
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,540
and I won't let you suffer.

133
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,680
Sweet talk.

134
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:08,040
Did I press too hard?

135
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:11,040
My shoulder hurts a little.

136
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,660
Is your shoulder hurt too?

137
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,000
No,

138
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,260
it's my lower back.

139
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,450
Your lower back?

140
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,760
Does it hurt?

141
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,090
It doesn't hurt.

142
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:32,840
It doesn't hurt.

143
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,770
It doesn't hurt.

144
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,540
I just feel like...

145
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:40,440
...I'm a jinx.

146
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:45,920
It seems everyone around me meets a terrible end.

147
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,440
Father did.

148
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:52,200
So did Yan'er.

149
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,400
Even Lord Jian and Sister Song.

150
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,970
I'm really afraid I'll bring you harm.

151
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,720
How could that be?

152
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:09,040
I'll give you a surprise when we get back,

153
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,920
and tell you everything.

154
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,640
What surprise?

155
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:20,000
I'll tell you when we return.

156
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,840
You're keeping it a secret?
